<BR>
<P>Werner Enterprises, Inc., is a truckload carrier of general commodities,
both inter- and intrastate commerce. The company, headquartered in Omaha, NE,
offers a number of transportation services. With strong financials and a
commitment to service, we are one of the nation's top five truckload carriers.
Premium equipment, superior technology and talented people help keep us ahead of
our competition. 
</P>
<P><IMG SRC="star_g~1.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="18">New! We have premium used
Werner trucks <A HREF="trk_sale.html">for sale</A>.</P></TD>
